data.description: ***HUGE 20K PRICE DROP*** This stunning JMC single-story home is nestled in the highly sought-after Whitney Ranch community. It offers not only beauty but also unbeatable proximity to schools, parks, shopping, and convenient freeway access.    Boasting three spacious bedrooms and three well-appointed full baths, this home ensures comfort and functionality. The kitchen is a chef's delight, featuring granite counters, a large island perfect for entertaining, a deep single kitchen sink, and upgraded stainless steel appliances.    The seamless flow of the great room concept, enhanced by built-in surround sound, is a testament to modern design and contemporary living. The expansive primary bedroom and ensuite bathroom are a private oasis, complete with a separate soaking tub and dual sinks. Embrace the perks of modern living, including a whole-house fan and owned solar, aligning with sustainability and cost-efficiency. Outside, the low-maintenance yards offer ample shade and easy upkeep, providing a tranquil outdoor space to unwind.    Residents of this community also have exclusive access to a clubhouse and pool, elevating the experience. Tucked away in a quiet neighborhood, this home offers stunning views of rolling hills, adding a touch of natural beauty to your daily lifestyle.
